Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的 他们俩全都是演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再见一次面的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次 根本没说话的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不擅长应付这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 能再见我几次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个月就好 能给我个机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往一个月看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊果然不行 果然喜欢不上 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远不如一上来就拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说我怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟不喜欢的女人交往 那是浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:14.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘つきなあなた 泣き虫のあたし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:20.60,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうして？ うまくいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:26.57,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オシャレした髪も ラインストーンの爪も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:32.47,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたは気付きもしないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:39.60,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LOVE 悲しい涙なんかじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:44.60,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目が乾いてヒリヒリするだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:50.86,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}転んでばっかり I LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:59.10,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを あたしだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:04.08,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}熱い想いを受け止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:11.27,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも つながってたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:16.10,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可愛くない泣き顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:18.12,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部愛してね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:14.70,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谎话连篇的你 爱哭鼻子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:20.60,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么进展得不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:26.57,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}精心打扮的头发 光彩夺目的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:32.47,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:39.60,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}love 并非悲伤的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:44.60,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:50.86,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:59.10,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:04.08,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:11.27,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:16.10,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:18.12,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周六晚上来我家住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 说句话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开玩笑么 拿我找乐？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母去札幌参加结婚典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次说想两个人出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是旅行 就像我们一整天都两人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天看电影 黄昏两个人高高兴兴地回家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(460,444)}Spaghetti Carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭吃意大利炭烧面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周做过所以不会做坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上妈妈来电话 和平时一样接就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴池已经提前擦得闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上 就是周末欣喜又心动的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 一边欣赏星空一边愉快地交谈到深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得17岁的少年少女不会有这样事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这不是矢野么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少见呀 来这边的店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 来买什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}避运套
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊 这种事无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说谎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 到早晨都把高桥紧紧地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧地拥抱 亲吻 再拥抱 直到早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥穿什么睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是穿睡衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这种露肩膀的就好了 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天快些到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连蹦带跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐车去车站前吗 还是等人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧 你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 尽量努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚某店的目击情报是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还特意去相邻街区 撞上了认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息传得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别净做些伤人的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少见的坦诚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 我正要上车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思没事我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不上车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关好门窗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上给你打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘带钥匙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 您慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也要赶紧出门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿今天成为特别的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她 叫也叫不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么推也推不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她 现在在重症监护病房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊 矢野总是很守时的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 接下电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 你和别人约好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 我稍微去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 都晚了30分钟了 怎么了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机也根本打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 刚出来就遇到些事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 还会再晚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能先回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 电影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概什么时候到家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫不清楚 你现在到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本的妈妈病倒了 我现在和她在医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不清楚 可能是中风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没从监护病房出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 真麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 没弄清病情前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么必须是你在那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就赶紧过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放着不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不管？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回家等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说高桥 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会回家 现在赶紧过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不来我就不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这样的日子 他选了山本同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得刚才就光是我在说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你有兄妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个弟弟 不过刚才说过…了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本联系不上她 打过去她也不接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我现在必须回医院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能帮我劝劝她么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的电话她就接了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊 现在赶快去高桥那不就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在干吗么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她孤身一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 虽说有 总跟女人在一起很少回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲戚也住在远处 没有能依靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人现在就妈妈一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种惴惴不安的感觉我很理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说啊 麻烦为什么要你照顾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 不要冒然同情才是为她好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没资格说我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在干的也是一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我现在回医院 拜托你联络了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我再打个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可留在那也不是办法啊 外面又冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 我不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我 傻瓜竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 明明不是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是拜托了 别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野为什么不理解我的心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野再求你也别打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无意义地坚持也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己不温柔也好 这些我都清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对方不是山本同学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能也不这么死板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不管怎样 只有今天希望你一定要来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 我讨厌这种时候一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内你从刚才就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是注意外面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家属请进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑波和其他都很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药物现在正在使血压恢复正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们发现得很及时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是压力和过度操劳引起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就快醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去办住院手续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你住这么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等她醒来再看情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来你不饿吗 没吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请你去食堂吃点儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 今天先回去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个必须去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的周末 留你真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我其实想等到阿姨醒来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有什么事不用介意给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然帮不上什么 精神上还是可以支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 今天真谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 帮我向阿姨问好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送 送你到门口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦 话说不快回去食堂就关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 给你出租车钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去车站前广场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳驾 我很急
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一场雪呀 要不今天怎么这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 真够冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带手套就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 哈气雪白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手套给你 戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 送给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 你朋友的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复同样的话题我也不介意 这种事要花时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你骂我最差劲了也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他说的一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有份无法停止的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口那堵着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就停那个红绿灯前面好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个碍事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借 过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃过无数次了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得这样对高桥最好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 你在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两情相悦？ 爱上别人的女友？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那全是 放你妈的屁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你在家等着 你怎么这么坚持呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算在这待到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能保证一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:22:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让高桥哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.00,0:25:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内 我一点儿也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.70,0:25:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么交往不伤害高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.50,0:25:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他的事 我能理解的比你多得多
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.10,0:25:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信赖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.20,0:25:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直缺少的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.10,0:25:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护高桥
